│                                                                               │
│ Reasoning:                                                                    │
│ - This function checks if a `TreeEntry` is a user of another `TreeEntry`.     │
│ - Ensure that gather nodes are correctly identified as users and their        │
│ `UserTreeIndices` are updated accordingly.                                    │
│                                                                               │
│ ### 5. Conclusion:                                                            │
│ The root cause of the issue is the missing or incorrect update of the         │
